comments: Yes, the beginning of the word would indicate the shape i.e. wop would be a donut shape, and the end of the word would indicate the colour i.e. isho was a sky blue. I made small notes for the spellings as ixa (yellow) and ixu (pink) sounded very similar. The task was difficult at first until noticed the pattern, and then trying to remember small differences as I think yellow was different dependent on the shape it was on
